[div class=p 
	"Now I don't think it will be fair to require Moons level of feedback to have those 3 bosses all published, because it's been little to no feedback so far, and it may not look very different and entertaining to the regulars (and future viewers). But it's still mostly because I do believe covering all the unique rooms in those 3 branches by beating the 3 different bosses - is how you can feature objectively different content in Standard.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=The current rules|href=/MovieRules#Standard)
	" don't dictate how different it has to be exactly. The Vault rules used to require at least 50% of inherently unique content, and that requirement got fired along with the Vault itself. These days we aim for what 
	[b 
		"makes sense
	]b
	", and I think having those 3 branches in Standard is the best idea.
	$LF
]div
